metadata.name: Animalia Lady Crane
metadata.description:
MATERIAL: A compilation of digital paint & vector art
SIZE: 5400*7200px
THE MAIN USED ELEMENTS: Demoiselle Crane, Yellow Merinque Flower, Protea Flower.

Crane bird's are large birds & humans don't domesticate  or keep them as pets, that means a "free specter". those are symbolic of luck & longevity. the main message of this power animal is "Dance & Pass (in your way through life)".
This NFT is my first NFT member in the Bird Garden collection and I have decided to develop and continue it. My main subject is the depiction of long-tailed birds in real-world landscapes full of flowers and plants, each symbolizing a concept with a very ancient background and history. Thank you for supporting and watching this work.
